Package ohos.aafwk.ability

Class FormBindingData

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.aafwk.ability.FormBindingData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Sequenceable

    public class FormBindingData
extends Object
implements Sequenceable
    Represents the data structure of a JS form.

    This class is used to carry the data to be passed for creating and updating a JS form.

    Since:
    5
